  "description": "<h1>Active: Mend</h1>Restores %replenish_health% health and %replenish_mana% mana to nearby allies, and removes most negative effects from the caster.<br><br>Radius: %replenish_radius%<br>Dispel Type: <span class=\"GameplayValues GameplayVariable\">Basic Dispel</span>\n\n<h1>Passive: Guardian Aura</h1> Grants %aura_health_regen% health regeneration and %aura_mana_regen% mana regeneration to allied units. If the wearer's health falls below %aura_bonus_threshold%%%, their health regeneration is increased to %aura_health_regen_bonus%. <br><br>Radius: %aura_radius% \nMovement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack.",
